text: Bash-Baybakovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Uryadinsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 58 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 14 km from Mishkino, 3 km from Uryady. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Bash-Baybakovo
